steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi007b" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi007b" display
When I add new column with Name "jitapicol007b" Type "string" for Table name "jitapi007b"
When I navigate to menu "API" with submenu "API endpoints"
Then I should see API screen display
When I create new group API with name "groupapi007b"
Then I should see group api "groupapi007b" displayed in api list
When I select api name "groupapi007b" from list
When I add new API endpoint
When I set endpoint of API to value "/v1/jitera/testing" in floating panel
When I set method of API to value "GET" in floating panel
